sign:The Deity Goes to the Palace of the Dragon King!
The Deity hhhhGoes to The hhhhhPalace of The hhhhhhhDragon King!
The Deity hhhhGoes to The hhhhhPalace of The hhhhhhhDragon King!
Nanami has just traveled back in time with the assistance of Mizuki's Route of Time.
In her quest to recover the Dragon King's right eye, she encountered the former Tomoe.
However, the Tomoe she has come to know and the one standing in front of her are two different beasts.
Is that... the Dragon King's eye?
Do you really think you can catch up on foot?
Are you sure you are a deity?
I should have known this Tomoe would not recognize me.
Where do you think he is going?
Well, he has fish and one of the Dragon King's eyes.
We need to get the eye back!
Maybe if we just explained the situation...
That is not going to work.
We have to wait for an opportunity and then snatch it.
You went all the way out there to get medicine for me?
But what I get in return is well worth it.
Take this, and you will surely get better.
He looks the same and sounds the same, but I barely recognize him.
Everything he is doing is for that woman.
Nanami-chan has probably never felt jealous, as I used to be.
The medicine is probably too hard to ingest like this.
I will go fetch some water from the spring.
Nanami-chan, are not you going to take the eye?
If I were you, I would not hesitate.
After all, that woman's an eyesore.
Just swallow this, and you will get better!
Did not you come here to get the eye back?
Why are you giving it to her?
Do you really want to give it to her?
But I cannot just sit by and watch a person suffer either!
She seems to have gotten better.
I cannot keep us here forever.
I cannot make him pay his dues from the past.
I have to pay it back with something from the present.
You would be wise not to make any sudden movements.
Your body is probably in pain.
It is not exactly happy with the stress of time travel.
Anyway, what is your plan now?
Do you think I could still find Isohime today?
What do you plan on doing?
If you give me the Dragon King's eye inside you, I will give you this in return.
She said I had the eye in me.
She offered to trade her clothes for it.
That might be the key to saving Tomoe.
You have a shop here of all places, Miss?
You can make any lady fall for you with just one bite of this!
Hm, I would not mind trading it for that gold ring you have there.
Crap, let us get out of here!
You have not changed in five-hundred years, have you?
I have to say, it did make finding you a cakewalk.
You will give me the Dragon King's eye?
This person's just a bit different from five-hundred years ago!
And that is not what I meant!
If the Dragon King's eye is really inside me, I want you to get it out for me.
You have one, though it is small.
Regardless of what you might think, my eye does not lie.
However, I would like to hear what I am getting in return.
As long as it is within my ability...
Can I have thirty years of your life?
You do not need to trust her, Nanami-chan.
Can you grab the eye yourself, then?
You do not even know where it is!
My eyes have a certain quality of clairvoyance to them!
There is nothing I cannot see!
This is a job for an adult.
Fine, you can have thirty years.
Thirty years will not kill me.
But Tomoe only has a day left.
She is not supposed to be able to do anything, so why is she choosing this path?
She keeps biting off more than she can chew.
I will let you pay later.
Relax, this will not take long.
I knew you had something much better to offer than your life.
You have the Dragon King's eye and the mark of the Earth Deity!
Do not mind if I help myself to both!
You should have listened to me, Nanami-chan.
Tomoe-kun's only reaping what he sowed.
There was no need for you to sacrifice yourself.
Nanami-chan, I do not understand you.
If you are so bent on helping people without even a familiar to protect you...
I will help you once more.
I can do to show you my loyalty.
The weight in my heart is lifting.
As long as I am with her,
I see that you have awoken, my new master..
I decided to be your new familiar!
You will be blown away by how much better I am!
Isohime, do not think that you can get away with harming my master.
The absolute power of her words...
This testament to my everlasting loyalty...
A sweet numbness is overcoming me...
The feeling of being ordered by a deity is splendid!
Bind me tighter with your invisible chains!
You basically just told me that you kissed me while I was asleep!
That is not exactly what happened, but at least you understand the situation.
So this is the Dragon King's eye?
The size and shape do not matter.
It is still the Dragon King's eye!
Let us hurry up and get it back to him!
I did not actually take anything!
Just take these and get out of here!
She gave us tickets to the Dragon Palace.
Letting her off like that was too nice of you.
I am glad that you did not actually do anything.
I would not kill someone in front of my master.
Tomoe-kun's probably feels the same way.
I do not want to soil my hands in front of you.
I am busy balancing my books!
The giant oyster we set up...
Man, I was so comfortable in there I fell asleep.
It is been a while has not it, Dragon King?
You have got some nerve showing your face in front of my master.
I cannot allow her to see anything gory.
So you really do ride a tortoise to the palace!
Nanami-chan, those windows only keep out the water.
Finally, I get to see my Tomoe again!
I wonder if Tomoe is still in love with Yukiji-san.
I am a bit scared to meet him.
I will probably just start comparing myself to her.
He was definitely nicer to her than he is to me.
He was so desperate to help her.
He is never been that way with me.
He will not even touch me.
No, I cannot worry about that right now!
I am losing what little motivation I have left!
Why is that your first suggestion?
Because you look like you do not want to go.
A member of the Dragon tribe?
Oh no, now every woman I see looks better than me!
What business does an Earth Deity have down here?
Someone important to me was taken away, so I am here to retrieve him.
Oh dear, I am sure he cannot wait to see you.
I am actually heading down there myself to drop off something for my dear husband.
May we both meet our dear ones soon.
The embroidery on that is beautiful!
This is a haori I made for him.
I spent seven days on it.
When we cannot see each other, I spend my time thinking about him.
I do not think I could make this if I spent ten years.
Mizuki, that woman's haori just got blown out!
We have to get it back!
The water has probably washed it far away by now.
That aside, the turbulence must be caused by the palace.
We need to get to the palace, though.
But you spent seven days on it!
Yes, and I enjoyed every minute of it.
That is more than enough for me.
Until just a moment ago, I was preoccupied with how my feelings were not being reciprocated.
He will not look me in the eye or lay a finger on me.
When did I get this passive?
It appears that something is amiss.
You guys explain to me what is going on here!
The fox we captured is going rampant!
The King is fighting him right now!
You are much more monstrous than you were before.
If that girl saw you now, she would be scared for the rest of her life.
She was begging me to let you go.
She was out of her mind.
She said she would get my eye back to save you.
She might be an Earth Deity but she is weak and helpless.
Wait, that girl was an Earth Deity?!
I thought she was your mis
Despite her looks, she is one.
One must not touch her so readily with bloodied hands like mine.
Why are you hiding in there again?!
I already know what is happening!
I went back to the past and met the old you.
I do not care if you do not share my feelings.
I do not care if you do not want to touch me.
I do not care if you love someone else.
I will not wait for things to go my way.
You do not have to look at me.
I will make you look at me.
Even if you do not look my way...
My feelings will not change for you.
That is enough to make me happy.
That girl is an Earth Deity?
She is just a kid no matter how you slice it.
Do you mind explaining to me what is going on here?
Were not you visiting your parents?!
You went after the demon fox again?
Have you not learned your lesson?
Have you forgotten the promise you made when you lost your right eye, perhaps?
There is an explanation for this!
Th-That Earth Deity came to give me my eye back!
Do not make fun of me!
What the hell is that rag?
Do you think I would even consider that crap?
Oh by the way, this was made with love by the person standing behind you.
Do not you think this is a fair trade for the fox?
I was just worried about my senior, that is all.
Well, I look forward to working with you, Tomoe-kun!
Let us all go home together!
we explore the story of how Tomoe became Mikage's familiar.
I wonder what their life together was like.
Next time, Tomoe becomes a familiar!
Also next time, The Deity Goes to a Mixer!
We have two stories next time!
